code: @Override public void run() {     try {         this.delegate.run().     } catch (UndeclaredThrowableException ex) {         this.errorHandler.handleError(ex.getUndeclaredThrowable()).     } catch (Throwable ex) {         this.errorHandler.handleError(ex).     } }
@Override public String toString() {     return "DelegatingErrorHandlingRunnable for " + this.delegate. }
